name: hangzhou typhoon
description:
hangzhou typhoon is the 5th song off my new beattape "souls" releaseing August 27, 2021. when i was forced to stay inside on a trip to hangzhou as the typhoon raged outside i wanted to create a song that had the feel of the typhoon. it was gnarly. 

the cover art was generated by AI using the text prompt "souls arriving." it looks like the souls have arrived at the gates of hell and are awaiting judgement. 

Bop your head and enjoy the music. If you purchase this piece, hit me up on twitter @ryanartwalker and I will send you the album with high quality AIFF files!
